{"id":"1cdcccff79a97c59fe2d8735df17e45e68be125b","url":"https://hub.baai.ac.cn/view/56475","title":"AI+NLP博士论文 | UC Berkeley 2026 | 内存高效的LLM推理算法 189页 - 智源社区","site_name":"TopHub","source":"Readhub · AI","byline":"图科学实验室Graph Science Lab\n                  2026-07-20 21:40 分享","excerpt":"生成式大语言模型（LLM）在语言处理中迅速崛起，但其高效推理面临严峻系统挑战。模型规模增速远超硬件内存提升，导致资源消耗剧增；同时，应用需求持续升级——要求更长上下文、更复杂推理及多轮agentic工作流，进一步加剧计算与内存压力。如何在有限硬件资源下实现低延迟、高吞吐、低成本的LLM服务，已成为当前系统研究的核心难题。","content_html":"<DIV class=\"page\" id=\"readability-page-1\"><div id=\"js_content\"><section nodeleaf=\"\"><mp-common-profile data-pluginname=\"mpprofile\" data-nickname=\"图科学实验室Graph Science Lab\" data-alias=\"Graph_Science_Lab\" data-from=\"0\" data-headimg=\"http://mmbiz.qpic.cn/mmbiz_png/2YZ1GHcDiaaLrod7BicMicB8ZxzJTEDXEHjEfeAnwSLK3I8ldIia9dQ3CeHY0jz78tyapw3R77wIM6weQD4XnJhJGg/0?wx_fmt=png\" data-signature=\"分享有关图理论、图表示学习、图神经网络、图+交叉学科（生物、化学、物理 ...）、图+交叉算法（DL、RL、NLP、CV ...）最新的科研资讯、论文、开源工具、招生/招聘、会议/竞赛、课程/书籍。欢迎持续关注。\" data-id=\"MzU4NTQyNjc5Mg==\" data-is_biz_ban=\"0\"></mp-common-profile></section><section nodeleaf=\"\"><img loading=\"lazy\" data-src=\"https://simg.baai.ac.cn/hub-detail/05949da86dd837934768eda023ddfb1a1784554811146.webp\" data-ratio=\"0.562962962962963\" data-s=\"300,640\" data-type=\"jpeg\" data-w=\"1080\" data-imgfileid=\"100008943\" data-aistatus=\"1\" src=\"https://simg.baai.ac.cn/hub-detail/05949da86dd837934768eda023ddfb1a1784554811146.webp\" referrerpolicy=\"no-referrer\"></section><p data-pm-slice=\"0 0 []\"><span dir=\"auto\"><span dir=\"auto\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\">生成式大型语言模型（</span></span><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\">generative Large Language Models,&#160;</span></span><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\">LLM）</span>作为一种强大的算法范式，在语言处理任务中迅速崛起，使得<span textstyle=\"\">高效（</span></span><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\">efficient</span></span><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\">）</span>的LLM推理成为一项重要的系统挑战。然而，LLM服务正变得越来越消耗资源，LLM模型规模的增长速度远远超过了<span textstyle=\"\">硬件内存</span>的增长速度，而应用程序也需要更长的上下文长度、更复杂的推理以及多轮</span><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\">agentic</span></span><span leaf=\"\">工作流。此外，LLM生成过程中固有的顺序依赖性意味着工作负载严重受限于内存带宽，从而为LLM推理造成了严重的内存瓶颈。这些挑战导致内存密集型LLM与内存受限的<span textstyle=\"\">硬件平台</span>之间日益加剧的瓶颈，限制了LLM的普及应用。</span></span></span></p><p><span dir=\"auto\"><span dir=\"auto\"><span leaf=\"\">为了应对这一挑战，本论文提出了几种<span textstyle=\"\">内存高效（</span></span><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\">memory-efficient</span></span><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\">）</span>的LLM推理算法，以支持处理具有长上下文长度的大型模型。首先，论文对LLM推理进行了性能分析和建模（第二章），指出LLM推理的主要瓶颈在于内存带宽而非计算能力，并发现随着上下文长度的增长，内存流量的主要来源从模型权重转移到了键值缓存。在此分析的基础上，论文第三章介绍了如何<span textstyle=\"\">量化模型权重（</span></span><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\">quantizing model weights</span></span><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\">）</span>以使其适应内存受限的GPU，第四章则提出了通过量化键值缓存激活来加速长上下文推理工作负载的方法。随后，论文概述了旨在仅从内存加载重要上下文来加速LLM推理的算法，并通过两个目标应用进行了验证：共享前缀工作负载（第五章）和推理工作负载（第六章）。最后，第七章总结了本论文的主要贡献，并展望了未来的研究方向。</span></span></span></p><section nodeleaf=\"\"><img loading=\"lazy\" data-src=\"https://simg.baai.ac.cn/hub-detail/098cfb9127f1cf7cc14279afc678191a1784554811147.webp\" data-ratio=\"1.4148148148148147\" data-s=\"300,640\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"1080\" type=\"block\" data-imgfileid=\"100014362\" data-aistatus=\"1\" src=\"https://simg.baai.ac.cn/hub-detail/098cfb9127f1cf7cc14279afc678191a1784554811147.webp\" referrerpolicy=\"no-referrer\"></section><section nodeleaf=\"\"><img loading=\"lazy\" data-aistatus=\"1\" data-imgfileid=\"100014363\" data-ratio=\"1.2944444444444445\" data-s=\"300,640\" data-src=\"https://simg.baai.ac.cn/hub-detail/b8fef0ce52725b203be0db0bf2968afc1784554811147.webp\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"1080\" type=\"block\" src=\"https://simg.baai.ac.cn/hub-detail/b8fef0ce52725b203be0db0bf2968afc1784554811147.webp\" referrerpolicy=\"no-referrer\"></section><p><strong><span leaf=\"\">论文题目<span textstyle=\"\">：</span></span></strong><span leaf=\"\">Memory-Efficient LLM Inference Algorithms</span><span leaf=\"\"><br></span></p><p><strong><span leaf=\"\">作者</span></strong><span leaf=\"\">：</span><span><span leaf=\"\">Coleman Hooper</span></span></p><p><strong><span leaf=\"\">类型：</span></strong><span><span leaf=\"\">2026年博士论文</span></span></p><p><strong><span leaf=\"\">学校：</span></strong><span><span leaf=\"\">University of California, Berkeley</span></span><span><span leaf=\"\">（美国加州大学伯克利分校</span></span><span><span leaf=\"\">）</span></span></p><section data-pm-slice=\"0 0 []\"><b><span face=\"等线\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\">下载论文</span></span></span></b><span face=\"等线\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\">：</span></span><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\">https://t.zsxq.com/IYhiE</span></span><span leaf=\"\"><br></span></span></section><p data-pm-slice=\"2 6 []\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\">请索引第143篇博士论文</span></span></p><table><tbody><tr><td data-colwidth=\"287\"><section nodeleaf=\"\"><img loading=\"lazy\" alt=\"图片\" data-aistatus=\"1\" data-imgfileid=\"100012752\" data-ratio=\"1.215625\" data-s=\"300,640\" data-src=\"https://simg.baai.ac.cn/hub-detail/3f102b0f72c9b6b948c795b4b440b13c1784554811147.webp\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"640\" type=\"block\" src=\"https://simg.baai.ac.cn/hub-detail/3f102b0f72c9b6b948c795b4b440b13c1784554811147.webp\" referrerpolicy=\"no-referrer\"></section></td><td data-colwidth=\"287\"><section nodeleaf=\"\"><img loading=\"lazy\" data-src=\"https://simg.baai.ac.cn/hub-detail/f67c44b0022bb6a9d8d0ecc2e16e3f761784554811148.webp\" alt=\"图片\" data-ratio=\"1.215625\" data-s=\"300,640\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"640\" type=\"block\" data-imgfileid=\"100012753\" data-aistatus=\"1\" src=\"https://simg.baai.ac.cn/hub-detail/f67c44b0022bb6a9d8d0ecc2e16e3f761784554811148.webp\" referrerpolicy=\"no-referrer\"></section></td></tr></tbody></table><section nodeleaf=\"\"><img loading=\"lazy\" data-src=\"https://simg.baai.ac.cn/hub-detail/26d9678958a35a9e499c39c6b0b865cb1784554811148.webp\" data-ratio=\"0.7462962962962963\" data-s=\"300,640\" data-type=\"png\